 Rising Leaders of Generation - NGO Website

## рџЊџ Overview
A comprehensive full-stack website for Rising Leaders of Generation NGO, featuring blog management, donation system, event management, gallery, and admin dashboard.

## рџљЂ Tech Stack

### Backend
- Node.js & Express.js
- MongoDB with Mongoose
- JWT Authentication
- Cloudinary for image upload
- Nodemailer for emails

### Frontend
- React.js
- Tailwind CSS
- Framer Motion for animations
- React Query for data fetching
- Font Awesome icons

